  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1186216">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1186216/" class="title-link">挺适合作教科书的</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1186216"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1201616/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1201616-25.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1201616/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">丁丁</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-07-29"
      class="main-meta">2007-07-29 21:41:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1186216_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  许先生一如既往的用他的理论，精耕农业、网络和文官体系来讲述中国历史，只不过这次讲的比较长，从头到尾了。大众读物，自然没什么深度，但学术性、思想性并不缺乏。此书作为中学教科书或者大学通识教育的教科书是在合适不过的了，最好能搭配着柏杨的《中国人史纲》来看，弥补...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
